{"tid":1849464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔入黎同今朝有出去黎明行動嘅手足講聲多謝","createTime":"2020-01-29T05:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T15:14:47.000Z","uid":31215,"like":179,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"bf072b35d18c5e0acaecb46dfb5c1487f1c686db","tid":1849464,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:30:41.000Z","msg":"多謝你地嘅付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有D人懶唔出、有D人唔認同今次行動，有D人有其他原因<br />\n但係唔可以否定有份參與嘅手足付出好多<br />\n早起、捱凍、俾狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論咩原因都唔可以單單打打落井下石<br />\n有D手足已經睇唔到我地講多謝<br />\n唔知幾時先放<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇出嘅連登仔快啲衝入黎多謝呢班手足<br />\n下次到你地參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f6c7a6c6205f4d3cfa7da3b75cd9c53cc817ba","tid":1849464,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:32:21.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5863c3b188f3a8984058156b08c5a9d97b9cea","tid":1849464,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e4d9cd85df39482c235724f6467bdd82e2a4a4","tid":1849464,"uid":31215,"l